item.title: IC Hockey Men’s 2s show the Medics who’s Boss
item.author: Benjamin Bell,
item.description: With an impressive 3-1 pre-season victory over RUMS 2nd XI last week, IC 2s arrived at Harlington keen to keep up the high standard of hockey and register a win in our first competitive fixture of the season. Having been defeated at the end of last season in a close-fought Varsity match, we were …
